title: 138: Turkey Day games and CFB picks
itunes:title: 138: Turkey Day games and CFB picks
description:
Former NFL scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks look ahead to the upcoming slate of critical matchups on Thanksgiving day. The duo also run down the college football schedule and make their game picks.
